1. Customers
	< view CUSTOMERs list >
	1. new customer (standard)
	2. filter by:
		1. customer
		2. site
	3. select customer [go to # CUSTOMER page]:
		< view CUSTOMER details: >
			< desc >
			< sites: >
				1. filter by:
					1. name
				2. select site [go to # SITE page]:
					< desc >
					< view SITE details: >
						< counts [sort by date] >
							1. select count [go to # COUNT page]:	
								< view COUNT details: >
									< summary >
									< zone hierarchy >
				3. new site 
					1. standard
					2. import item pack
					3. import item [IMPORT SINGLE ITEM dialog]
					4. new item [NEW ITEM dialog]
														
			< edit customer: >
				edit each field (name / pic / etc.)
			< enable/disable customer [never delete to avoid risk] >


2. Items
	< view ITEMs >
		1. filter by:
			1. name
		2. select item [ITEM dialog]
			< ITEM dialog >
				1. edit
				2. clone
				3. add to packs
		3. new item
	< view ITEM PACKs >
		1. filter by:
			1. name
			2. item within it
		2. select item pack [go to # ITEM PACK PAGE]
			< view ITEM PACK >
				1. edit
				2. clone
				3. new item [IMPORT ITEM dialog]
				4. import item [IMPORT SINGLE ITEM dialog]
				5. import from item pack [IMPORT ITEMS dialog]
					< IMPORT ITEMS dialog >	
						1. 	select item pack -> 
							list items [checkboxes=checked] ->
							let user edit ->
							submit
		3. new item pack


